<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>TWZ</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 14:24:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>伊朗袭击货船后暂停通过霍尔木兹海峡的船只计划</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/plan-to-move-ships-through-strait-of-hormuz-paused-after-iran-strikes-cargo-vessel</link><description>&lt;p&gt;霍尔木兹海峡最近发生的一系列行动是在航运再次开始流经该海峡时发生的。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/plan-to-move-ships-through-strait-of-hormuz-paused-after-iran-strikes-cargo-vessel"&gt;伊朗袭击货船后暂停通过霍尔木兹海峡的船舶运输计划&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 00:10:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/plan-to-move-ships-through-strait-of-hormuz-paused-after-iran-strikes-cargo-vessel</guid></item><item><title>具有讽刺意味的是，白宫想要突袭海军 E-2 账户来支付美国空军 E-7 的费用</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/in-an-ironic-turn-of-events-white-house-wants-to-raid-navy-e-2-account-to-pay-for-usaf-e-7s</link><description>&lt;p&gt;五角大楼曾试图取消 E-7 并增加 E-2 机队，然后史诗狂怒行动发生了。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/in-an-ironic-turn-of-events-white-house-wants-to-raid-navy-e-2-account-to-pay-for-usaf-e-7s"&gt;具有讽刺意味的是，白宫想要突袭海军 E-2 帐户来支付美国空军 E-7 的费用，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 23:22:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/in-an-ironic-turn-of-events-white-house-wants-to-raid-navy-e-2-account-to-pay-for-usaf-e-7s</guid></item><item><title>视频疯传，波音 777 飞行员驾驶波音喷气式飞机进行极低飞行</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/boeing-777-pilots-take-on-extremely-low-pass-by-boeing-jet-captured-in-viral-video</link><description>&lt;p&gt;当飞机在跑道上空以非常低的高度倾斜时，其巨大机翼的尖端距地面仅几英尺。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/boeing-777-pilots-take-on-extremely-low-pass-by-boeing-jet-captured-in-viral-video"&gt;病毒视频中捕捉到的波音 777 飞行员驾驶波音喷气式飞机进行极低飞行的视频&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 20:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/boeing-777-pilots-take-on-extremely-low-pass-by-boeing-jet-captured-in-viral-video</guid></item><item><title>美国空军希望拥有射程高达 1,000 英里的空对空导弹</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-wants-air-to-air-missile-with-a-whopping-1000-mile-range</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国空军希望通过真正的“杀伤网”武器来超越其最新、最强大的空对空导弹能力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-wants-air-to-air-missile-with-a-whopping-1000-mile-range"&gt;美国空军想要射程高达 1,000 英里的空对空导弹&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 18:32:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/usaf-wants-air-to-air-missile-with-a-whopping-1000-mile-range</guid></item><item><title>特朗普将批准为土耳其卡恩战斗机出售重要的 F110 涡轮风扇发动机</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/trump-set-to-clear-critical-f110-turbofan-engine-sale-for-turkeys-kaan-fighter</link><description>&lt;p&gt;期待已久的转让将使土耳其的卡恩战斗机保持在正轨，同时引发人们对 F-35 是否重返谈判桌的猜测。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/trump-set-to-clear-critical-f110-turbofan-engine-sale-for-turkeys-kaan-fighter"&gt;特朗普准备批准土耳其卡恩战斗机关键 F110 涡轮风扇发动机销售的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 16:17:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/trump-set-to-clear-critical-f110-turbofan-engine-sale-for-turkeys-kaan-fighter</guid></item><item><title>奋进号航天飞机在其“全栈”荣耀中看起来绝对令人难以置信</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/space-shuttle-endeavour-looks-absolutely-incredible-in-all-its-full-stack-glory</link><description>&lt;p&gt;奋进号是有史以来建造的最后一架航天飞机，其展示的效果是独一无二的，其结果令人瞠目结舌。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/space-shuttle-endeavour-looks-absolutely-incredible-in-all-its-full-stack-glory"&gt;奋进号航天飞机在其“全栈”荣耀中看起来绝对令人难以置信，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 23:04:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/space-shuttle-endeavour-looks-absolutely-incredible-in-all-its-full-stack-glory</guid></item><item><title>撤离仍因霍尔木兹海峡关闭而搁浅的数百艘船只的计划正在合并</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/plan-to-evacuate-hundreds-of-ships-still-stranded-from-strait-of-hormuz-closure-is-coalescing</link><description>&lt;p&gt;霍尔木兹海峡仍然是一条极其紧张的水道，未来一段时间内交通将无法正常通过。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/plan-to-evacuate-hundreds-of-ships-still-stranded-from-strait-of-hormuz-closure-is-coalescing"&gt;《撤离霍尔木兹海峡关闭后仍滞留的数百艘船只的计划正在合并》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 18:06:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/plan-to-evacuate-hundreds-of-ships-still-stranded-from-strait-of-hormuz-closure-is-coalescing</guid></item><item><title>看不见的 MQ-1 掠食者袖珍机队仍在以专业角色飞行</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/pocket-fleet-of-mq-1-predators-still-serving-navy-test-community</link><description>&lt;p&gt;前空军 MQ-1“捕食者”无人机已经悄然获得了第二次生命。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/pocket-fleet-of-mq-1-predators-still-serving-navy-test-community"&gt;未见的 MQ-1 捕食者袖珍舰队仍在以专业角色飞行后&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 17:04:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/pocket-fleet-of-mq-1-predators-still-serving-navy-test-community</guid></item><item><title>MQ-28“幽灵蝙蝠”无人机在太平洋大部队作战演习中首次亮相</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/mq-28-ghost-bat-drone-debuts-in-large-force-combat-exercise-in-the-pacific</link><description>&lt;p&gt;MQ-28 正在参加“勇敢之盾”计划，让我们可以一睹它和其他 CCA 如何融入未来的联合行动。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/mq-28-ghost-bat-drone-debuts-in-large-force-combat-exercise-in-the-pacific"&gt;MQ-28“幽灵蝙蝠”无人机在太平洋大部队作战演习中&lt;/a&gt;首次亮相&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;首先出现。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 16:45:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/mq-28-ghost-bat-drone-debuts-in-large-force-combat-exercise-in-the-pacific</guid></item><item><title>北约和乌克兰求助私营部门帮助俄罗斯火山口机场</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/nato-and-ukraine-turning-to-private-sector-to-help-crater-russian-airfields</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一项新的挑战为任何能够开发出阻止俄罗斯使用其机场的系统的人提供了奖励。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/nato-and-ukraine-turning-to-private-sector-to-help-crater-russian-airfields"&gt;北约和乌克兰求助私营部门帮助俄罗斯火山口机场的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;TWZ&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 19:43:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/nato-and-ukraine-turning-to-private-sector-to-help-crater-russian-airfields</guid></item></channel></rss>